{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Have you ever imagined waking up one day to find yourself transported to a world filled with magic and strange creatures, embarking on a thrilling adventure?</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Have you ever fantasized about playing different roles in this world, either as a hero defending it or as a villain destroying it?</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Now, the opportunity has arrived! Enter the God Chosen Place!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Meticulously Crafted Script</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To ensure you experience a range of emotions in the game\u2014whether it\u2019s excitement, sadness, joy, or heroism\u2014I have repeatedly revised the outline. Each part of the story has been carefully considered for its logic and potential for development.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the story, you will meet characters with different personalities. Some will become your friends, while others will become your enemies. If you observe closely, you\u2019ll discover that villains are not inherently evil; they may have pasts unknown to others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/\u70ed\u8840\u5267\u60c5.gif?t=1733616684\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Make Your Choice</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the story, you will encounter many choices. Some may seem insignificant, while others could impact the plot later on. A small decision might change a character\u2019s fate, but who knows? Perhaps that seemingly trivial choice will alter everything in the God Chosen Place\u2026</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/\u9009\u62e9\u52a8\u56fe.gif?t=1733616684\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Easy-to-Learn Combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Simple and easy-to-learn turn-based combat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Equip your magic, buy your items, and in battle, just click to use them. Too much hassle to click? No problem, pressing a button on your keyboard works just as well!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">What if you encounter an enemy you can\u2019t defeat? Hmm\u2026 then fight weaker enemies to level up!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/\u6218\u6597\u52a8\u56fe.gif?t=1733616684\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Manage Your Organization</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Is the story too intense? Too sad? No way! I need a break!</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Recruit NPCs and have them work for you to earn more gold. Why earn gold? As the saying goes, \u201cA man without lofty ambitions is like a bird without wings!\u201d With gold, you can recruit more mercenaries! With more mercenaries, you can conquer territories in the Fierce Battlefield! Train them and turn them into a formidable army!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Worried that managing might be too complicated?</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Don\u2019t be! To let you better experience the ups and downs of the story, the management part is simplified for easy management!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/\u62db\u751f\u52a8\u56fe.gif?t=1733616684\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Relaxing and Fun Mini-Games</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features numerous mini-games. Spend your free time hunting, singing, drinking, honing your swordsmanship, or running. While relaxing, you can also earn more gold.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642220/extras/\u5c0f\u6e38\u620f\u52a8\u56fe.gif?t=1733616684\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Easy Map Navigation</strong></h2><p cla